      <title>民主党考虑提前提名拜登，以压制交换谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/democrats-weigh-early-biden-nomination-to-squash-talk-of-a-swap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党全国委员会正考虑最早在 7 月中旬正式提名乔·拜登，以确保总统能够出现在 11 月的选票上，同时有助于消除在上周辩论表现不佳后党内关于更换他的传言。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/democrats-weigh-early-biden-nomination-to-squash-talk-of-a-swap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:11:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅内德斯的妹妹称家中存放现金是“古巴特有的习俗”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/bob-menendez-s-sister-said-cash-kept-in-house-is-a-cuban-thing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯的姐姐在其腐败案审判中作证称，他们的古巴家人长期持有现金，这支持了他的说法，即他在家中存放现金，并且联邦调查局特工查获的近 50 万美元并非来自非法贿赂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/bob-menendez-s-sister-said-cash-kept-in-house-is-a-cuban-thing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:08:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛里塔尼亚总统加祖阿尼赢得第二任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/mauritania-president-wins-second-term-in-emerging-gas-producer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛里塔尼亚总统穆罕默德·乌尔德·加祖阿尼在周六的选举中赢得第二任期，该国准备在第三季度生产出第一批天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/mauritania-president-wins-second-term-in-emerging-gas-producer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱首次出访巴西，选择参加支持博索纳罗的集会，而非支持卢拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/milei-picks-pro-bolsonaro-rally-over-lula-for-first-brazil-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱终于首次访问了该国最大的贸易伙伴巴西。但这位自由主义者不会与总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦会面，而是会与左翼总统的最大竞争对手会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/milei-picks-pro-bolsonaro-rally-over-lula-for-first-brazil-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:03:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的豁免权胜利也帮助拜登转移了人们对辩论混乱的注意力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/trump-s-immunity-win-also-helps-biden-distract-from-debate-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院裁定唐纳德·特朗普享有一定的刑事起诉豁免权，特朗普在政治和法律上取得了重大胜利 — — 但这给他陷入困境的对手乔·拜登总统带来了好处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/trump-s-immunity-win-also-helps-biden-distract-from-debate-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:00:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
